data.description: This amazing home is located in north Denton, just minutes from TX Women's University, on an oversized corner lot and has tons of potential. Inside of the home boasts 3 bed and 2 bath, tile countertops in kitchen and both baths, wood floors, and built in shelving in living room. The expansive dining area has potential to be split up into two separate spaces as well for an additional living area. Mature trees provide excellent shade, wood deck in the back, storage building, and more. Property in need of some updating and clean up, but priced WELL BELOW similar homes in the neighborhood. All you need is a vision and a plan to make this property a STUNNER with this deeply discounted list price.
